Detailed Description

template<class AttributeType, class InputDBFormat>
class InitKey< AttributeType, InputDBFormat >

Functor used to intialize the not redundant mining.

This functor is used to search the attributes of the database.

The template parameter AttributeType is the type of the attributes. The template parameter InputDBFormat is the type of the database.
